review:
Bought this in November but only started using it about 3 months ago.

First Impression: Lovely form factor, sleek, rich finish.

PROS: Bought this with basic specs. ie. 4GB/500GB Hard drive etc
1. Boots like a beast, maybe less than 5 secs;
2. Its fast when multi-tasking, i.e working on documents, surfing internet, listening to music;
3. Very quiet;
4. Gorgeous display, movies look phenomenal (Have KODI installed);
5. Windows 10 is slick and fluid with this machine;
6. Wireless works great;
7. Copying large files to my USB drive, ie over 5GB movies are amazingly fast.

CON:
The volume is at a 100% but its too low for me. I listen to my music and movies pretty loud so even though it sounds clear, the volume could have been louder so now I need to buy a headphones with volume control or amplifier. ASUS could have done a bit better as Ive had DELLs before and the volume was great but this one is just low for my tastes. For some, the loudness may be sufficient.

All in all, would have given this five stars but the volume is a dealbreaker for me that is.
